body: This removes the old and badly documented/designed shared key cache from DHT.c and moves the implemenation to a separate file. This makes it more testable and allows a better overview of how many caches exist (currently 7, total ~0,5MB). Additionally I think this fixes several missed `crypto_memzero` calls. --- This change is [](https://reviewable.io/reviews/toktok/c-toxcore/2317)
